title: Iwin Games - Syberia 1 - Adventure - Wendy99
description:
SYBERIA 1 - PRECRACKED INSTALLER

Kate Walker, a young ambitious lawyer from New York, is handed what seems a fairly straight forward assignment - a quick stop over to handle the sale of an old automaton factory hidden in the alpine valleys, then straight back home to the US.
Little did she imagine when embarking on this task that her life would be turned upside down. On her expedition across Europe, traveling from Western Europe to the far reaches of Eastern Russia, she encounters a host of incredible characters and locations in her attempt to track down Hans, the genius inventor - the final key to unlock the secret of Syberia.
